title: Fantasy Matches Made in Heaven (Draft Edition!) | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We take a look at the upcoming NFL draft through a fantasy lens, examining the biggest skill-position names on the board and predicting where they will get drafted, where they should get drafted, and which destination would be the unlikeliest.
Host: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
